 AADL Protocol (AI Agent Decision Logging)
Version 1.0

Standard data format:
- Decision ID
- Timestamp
- Agent identifier
- Decision type
- Input context
- Options considered
- Option chosen
- Optimization function weights
- Trade-offs made (what was deprioritized)
- Confidence score
- Outcome (if known)

Standard API endpoints:
- GET /decisions (query decision history)
- GET /decisions/{id} (get specific decision details)
- GET /optimization (current optimization function)
- POST /feedback (provide outcome data)

Standard metadata:
- Agent capabilities
- Optimization dimensions
- Constraint parameters
